## Stack
- `apps/orchestrator/` — FastAPI, LangGraph, AsyncSqliteSaver, APScheduler, vault watcher, `blackbox` CLI
- `apps/dashboard/` — Next.js 14, React Flow, Zustand, WebSocket
- `vault/` — skills in `.system/skill-definitions/`, triggers in `.system/trigger-rules/`
- **Skills (9):** lead_gen, summarize_meeting, weekly_review (Python graphs) +
  YAML pipelines: summarize_note, inbox_triage, supplier_intake, client_brief,
  follow_up_draft (all vault_fs), supplier_research (needs search driver enabled)
- **Drivers:** vault_fs (enabled) · search (Serper/Tavily via
  `tools/search_server.py`, ships `enabled: false` — set SERPER_API_KEY or
  TAVILY_API_KEY and flip `enabled` in drivers.json) · fs/shell npx examples (off)
- **Autonomy:** drop any note into `00-Inbox/` → `inbox-note-summarize` trigger runs
  summarize_note (meeting-tagged notes go to the meeting rule via `not_tags` exclusion);
  budget-deferred runs queue in the IVT and resume when the gate clears

